data.description: This 10-bedroom, 5-bathroom duplex, presents a promising opportunity for investors and homeowners alike. With a spacious living area and a modern kitchen in each unit, it caters to owner/tenant comfort and convenience. The property's strategic location in Minneapolis enhances its rental potential, and its 10 bedrooms offer versatility in accommodating various tenant needs. This duplex provides both space and functionality in a sought-after market.
